dismissalText.commentary: Anneke Bosch c †Healy b Brown 0 (3b 0x4 0x6 7m) SR: 0

dismissalComment.html: straight up and out! Terrific bowling from Brown. Bosch given a working over the by the extra bounce. Short of a length at the body, fends it off the shoulder of the bat into the cordon and Healy does the work with the gloves. That was a very old-school WACA dismissal

dismissalText.commentary: Tazmin Brits lbw b Sutherland 5 (48b 0x4 0x6 56m) SR: 10.41

dismissalComment.html: huge appeal for lbw given not out. Australia review. This nipped back past the inside edge and hit the back leg in front of off. Height is the only query. No bat involved. Smashing the top of middle! Three reds. Brits is out. Australia have a third. Great delivery from Sutherland, nipping back off the seam
